            <hi rend="italic">Placement of text:</hi> handle of the mirror-shaped panel, under the rosette.
             <hi rend="italic">Letterheights:</hi> 0.005.</p>
            </div>
          <div>
            <head>Text:</head>
            <p><hi rend="italic">Origin of text:</hi> Chersonesos. 
              <hi rend="italic">Document type:</hi> Dedication.  
              <hi rend="italic">Date:</hi> 14th cent. 
              <hi rend="italic">Dating criteria:</hi> Visual decoration; language.</p>
            <p><hi rend="italic">Editions:</hi> unpublished.</p>
            
            <p>Υ</p>
          </div>
          
